data.description: Don't miss this charming, furnished, 3-bedroom home with mature landscaping offering incredible curb appeal. Nestled just minutes away from five golf courses, nearby to shopping, movie theater, endless bike trails, and more! Step inside to find a spacious floor plan with tall, vaulted ceilings, and large windows throughout bringing in tons of natural light. The large backyard features a covered patio and mature trees, providing the perfect setting for relaxation and outdoor activities with a stunning mountain view. This property is a family estate sale, ready for immediate occupancy. Sold in as-is condition with furnishings included. Televisions, some wall art/photos, and personal belongings in closets excluded. Washer & dryer negotiable. Buyer to verify all information, deemed reliable, however buyer to verify all info including utilities, rental restrictions, and HOA information if applicable. The listing Broker's offer of compensation is made only to participants of the MLS where the listing is filed.
